ind p√• www.mycruise.dk ‚Äì er du nysgerrig p√• at se, hvem vi er, s√• kan du ‚Äùm√∏de‚Äù os her: https://www.mycruise.dk/team','https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/4256672236/','2025-07-01',1,NULL,'[\"Budgetprognoser\", \"Budgettering\", \"Finansiel rapportering\", \"Kontoafstemning\", \"Likviditet\", \"Prognosticering\", \"Regnskab\", \"Regnskabsopg√∏relser\", \"Strategic Financial Management\", \"√òkonomisk planl√¶gning\"]',NULL,'2025-07-01 09:13:04','2025-07-01 09:13:04'),(203,4258603030,'KHR Architecture s√∏ger bygningskonstrukt√∏rpraktikanter',110,'K√∏benhavn, Region Hovedstaden, Danmark','Om jobbet\n\nBygningskonstrukt√∏rpraktikanter til KHR Architecture [English version below]\n\nVi er en innovativ tegnestue, som anvender de nyeste v√¶rkt√∏jer, metoder og softwarel√∏sninger til at l√∏se vores mange opgaver. I √∏jeblikket arbejder vi med en r√¶kke forskellige st√∏rre og mindre projekter i b√•de ind- og udland, bl.a. hospitals-, skole-, erhvervs- og boligprojekter, som du vil have mulighed for at stifte n√¶rmere bekendtskab med.\n\nVi Kan Tilbyde Dig\n\n\net praktikophold p√• en af landets √¶ldste tegnestuer, hvor du vil indg√• i et projektteam p√• lige fod med et hold af vores faglige dygtige medarbejdere.\nh√∏j grad af medbestemmelse og involvering i tegnestuens mange sp√¶ndende arbejdsopgaver og processer.\nmulighed for at bruge din viden fra studiet i praksis i forbindelse med tegnestuens projekter.\nmulighed for at f√• indblik i arbejdet med bygherrer√•dgivning, da tegnestuen ogs√• har en afdeling for bygherrer√•dgivning.\nudsigt over vandet, l√¶kker frokostordning samt sociale og faglige arrangementer.\n\n\nVi Forventer At Du\n\n\ner ansvarlig, engageret og selvt√¶nkende.\nbesidder gode samarbejdsevner.\nhar et godt kendskab til projektering i Revit.\ner flydende p√• enten dansk eller engelsk - ideelt set p√• begge sprog\n\n\nVores tegnestue er beliggende i det historiske og natursk√∏nne Holmen, der ogs√• er kendt for sit kreative studiemilj√∏. Praktikopholdet er p√• 37 timer om ugen inklusive en betalt frokostpause og gratis frokost.\n\nEr du interesseret, s√• send dit CV og portfolio ved at klikke p√• ANS√òG NU knappen. Husk at n√¶vne, hvorn√•r og hvor l√¶nge, du kan v√¶re i praktik. Har du sp√∏rgsm√•l, er du velkommen til at kontakte konstrukt√∏r Mads Sydow p√• mail msy@khr.dk eller telefon +45 2427 4503.\n\nEnglish Version\n\nArchitectural technologist interns\n\nWe are an innovative architectural company that uses the latest tools, methods and software solutions to solve our many projects. We are currently working on a variety of large and small projects, including hospital, school, commercial and residential projects, which you will have the opportunity to become more familiar with.\n\nWe Offer You\n\n\nan internship at one of the country\'s leading design firms, where you will become part of a project team with skilled colleagues\na high degree of participation and involvement in the our projects and processes\nthe opportunity to put your knowledge from your studies into practice in the context of the KHR projects\nthe opportunity to gain insight into the work with client consultancy, as our company also has a client consultancy department\na view over the water, free lunch and regular social and professional events.\n\n\nWe Expect You To\n\n\nbe responsible, committed and a self-starter.\npossess good interpersonal skills.\nhave a good knowledge of design in Revit.\nhave good level of either English or Danish, ideally both.\n\n\nOur architecture studio is located in the historic and scenic Holmen, which is also known for its creative studio environment. The internship is 37 hours per week including a paid lunch and lunchbreak.\n\nIf you are interested, please send your CV by clicking on the APPLY NOW button. Please mention when and for how long you could join us. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact Mads Sydow at msy@khr.dk or +45 2427 4503.','https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/4258603030/'