l for CTO/Co-Founder: Building the Hybrid Intelligence World Platform and Driving Global Scaling',188,'K√∏benhavn, Region Hovedstaden, Danmark','Om jobbet\n\nAre you a visionary technologist with a passion for human-machine/AI collaboration? Are you convinced we need to ensure Responsible AI and Safe AI in tech integrations? Do you think science/research and upskilling are the essential routes to ensure such Responsible AI and Safe AI implementations? Are you ready to build and scale a revolutionary product with Generative AI to reshape both education and science services? \n\n\n\n\nHybrid Intelligence World, founded by Dr. Carina Antonia Hallin in February 2023, is an on-demand platform and marketplace for the bundling of science/research, education/upskilling, and tech integration for organizational transformations in the human-machine age. It aims to be one of the frontrunners of the next human-machine frontier, where the symbiotic relationship between human and machines/artificial intelligence unlocks unprecedented potential. With our top expert solvers, we also work to integrate Ethical AI and Responsible AI with clients. The Hybrid Intelligence World Market is experiencing explosive growth, projected to reach US$74 billion by 2032, with a CAGR of 22%. \n\n\n\n\nWe\'ve established the foundation, a board, and the ‚Äòvision‚Äô. We\'ve also developed an MVP, and we are now in the process of building version 2.0 of the platform for global sales launch. We\'re seeking a dynamic and experienced CTO/Co-Founder to lead our technical vision and strategy, taking our platform to its next level of scalability and spearheading our sales expansion. \n\n\n\n\nLocation: Copenhagen, Holte, Denmark (Hybrid/Remote options available)\n\nApplication Deadline: July 22, 2025 \n\n\n\n\nThe Opportunity\n\nThis is a unique opportunity to shape the technological backbone of a company poised for significant disruption with the purpose that all organizations must be science/research and upskilling based as AI transforms the global economy. As our CTO/Co-Founder, you will be instrumental in: Defining and executing the technical roadmap: From architectural design to technology stack decisions, you will own the end-to-end technical strategy, ensuring our platform is scalable, secure, and future-proof. Building and leading a world-class engineering team: You will recruit, mentor, and inspire a team of exceptional engineers‚Äîboth internal and in collaboration with our tech solvers/organizations on the platform, employing more than 5,000 engineers globally‚Äîfostering a culture of innovation, collaboration, and excellence. Driving product innovation: Working hand-in-hand with the Co-CEO and product team, you\'ll translate market needs and user feedback into cutting-edge features and functionalities that maintain our competitive edge. Ensuring seamless integration with sales and business development: You will be a key voice in communicating our technical capabilities to investors, partners, and customers, understanding their needs, and ensuring our product can be effectively sold and adopted. Overseeing data strategy, security, and quality assurance: You will be responsible for robust data management, privacy, and the highest standards of quality across our platform. Championing the \"hybrid\" philosophy: You\'ll embody the core principles of hybrid intelligence, ensuring our technology empowers humans and prioritizes ethical AI development. \n\n\n\n\nWho You Are \n\nA seasoned technologist: You possess a deep understanding of AI, machine learning, and scalable software architecture, with hands-on experience building and deploying complex systems. A visionary leader: You can articulate a clear technical vision and inspire a team to achieve it. You are comfortable leading from the front, yet also know when to empower your team. A strategic thinker: You can align technical decisions with overarching business goals, understanding how technology drives sales and market penetration. An entrepreneurial spirit: You thrive in the ambiguity and fast pace of a startup, are resourceful, and possess a \"get it done\" attitude. Previous startup experience is a significant plus. Sales-aware and customer-centric: While primarily technical, you understand the sales cycle, the importance of product-market fit, and how to translate technical features into compelling value propositions for customers. A strong communicator: You can effectively communicate complex technical concepts to both technical and non-technical audiences, from engineers to investors and potential clients. \n\n\n\n\nWhy Join Hybrid Intelligence World? \n\nBe at the forefront of tech transformation and hybrid intelligence research: Work on cutting-edge technology in collaboration with researchers and tech solvers in their fields to revolutionize how humans and AI collaborate, with the intention to advance and scale human and organizational consciousness. Meaningful impact: Build a product that empowers individuals and organizations, driving efficiency, creativity, and ethical decision-making. Significant equity: As a co-founder, you will have substantial equity in a rapidly growing platform. Growth potential: Play a pivotal role in scaling a global business in a dynamic market. Join a passionate and dedicated team committed to making a real difference. If you are ready to architect the future of hybrid intelligence and lead our technological scaling alongside our sales growth, we want to hear from you. \n\n\n\n\nTo apply, please send your resume and a compelling cover letter outlining your relevant experience, motivation, and your vision for Hybrid Intelligence World to hello@hybridintelligence.world by July 22, 2025','https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/view/4256294486/','2025-06-30',48,NULL,'[\"Kunstig intelligens\", \"Softwareudvikling\", \"Webtjenester\", \"IT-strategi\", \"Maskinl√¶ring\", \"Mobilapplikationer\", \"Software Architecture\", \"Strategi\", \"Strategisk